{"tid":273772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估地方）人妻搭嘟嘟車遭輪流性侵　女嬰被拋出車外慘死","createTime":"2017-06-06T23:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T03:08:46.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6736919e3b40d9615c674745a94c908f432b6474","tid":273772,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:53:01.000Z","msg":"新德里郊區一名23歲女子與丈夫吵架後，帶著9個月大女兒要返回娘家，不料她才登上嘟嘟車就被司機和男乘客們騷擾，當她的女兒大哭時，他們把女嬰拋出車外，再輪流性侵女子。<br />\n<br />\n慘案發生在古爾岡（Gurgaon），被害人與丈夫吵架後，於5月29日午夜乘坐嘟嘟車打算返回娘家，當時車上除了司機，還有兩名男子。她上車後，三人開始騷擾她，見被害人9個月大的女兒哭鬧，三人便將女嬰拋出車外，導致女嬰頭部重創慘死。<br />\n被害人報警時，只提及女嬰遭人扔出嘟嘟車，後來才告知警方自己也遭輪流性侵，但她拒絕接受化驗。警方暫時把案件列作輪姦及謀殺案處理，目前已扣留多人問話。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170607/1134565/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170607%2F1134565%2F&d=wJ5LuFgkAU8mwrfKeu97FE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=14659739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170607/1134565/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/075225_6921c4dded731c175371b9d2988417e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F075225_6921c4dded731c175371b9d2988417e5.jpg&h=15ad99ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b421d01eb1af554c33cf7e89ed7234c79e71a761","tid":273772,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:58:19.000Z","msg":"係咪所有印度男人都係受自己精蟲感染的人形十三使徒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da5e0954342e4debd4b8246319d19a62d622054","tid":273772,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:58:35.000Z","msg":"好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3a0b2c7494